ce:section.ce:para:
The CMC of GPTD was measured by the pyrene probe method as described in previous work [29]. Fluorescence intensity ratio at 373 and 384 nm (I373/I384
                        ) against the logarithm of GPTD concentrations (Log C) was plotted, and the CMC of GPTD was calculated by the crossover point where I373/I384
                         decreased rapidly.
